{"tid":2043229,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[丹超] 閉門作賽下，安排現場球迷入場觀戰。","createTime":"2020-05-30T09:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:43:07.000Z","uid":124655,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3461dd904acfdbf0c5da5eb6a3942ce95d6dc965","tid":2043229,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343058864553463808.jpeg/UwDBQBrmEk3LvnTuYrevMJblpG-vSG3JnrtSh567Uoc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343058864553463808.jpeg%2FUwDBQBrmEk3LvnTuYrevMJblpG-vSG3JnrtSh567Uoc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=77055192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨德甲重開賽季，歐洲球壇亦逐步回復生氣，丹麥超級聯賽成為歐洲第二個在新冠肺炎疫情下復賽的聯賽。有別於德甲的閉門作賽，老牌球會阿侯斯（AGF Aarhus）以閉門方式容納近一萬名「現場觀眾」。<br />\n<br />\n隨新冠肺炎在歐洲地區的疫情放緩，各地停擺的聯賽亦逐步復賽，各地聯賽重開後，各出奇謀增添球場內的氣氛，正如德甲慕遜加柏在主場放置球迷的卡板，而韓職的FC首爾更以吹氣娃娃充當球迷。<br />\n<br />\n在丹麥超級聯賽復賽首仗，阿侯斯主場對蘭達斯（Randers FC）的賽事，竟然在閉門作賽下，安排現場球迷入場觀戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343033320139001856.jpeg/QHipJAdek4Izox3UshH5eMbEFS7zaq_Ngw0wxYMNMMU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343033320139001856.jpeg%2FQHipJAdek4Izox3UshH5eMbEFS7zaq_Ngw0wxYMNMMU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8cdf55ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343033738336276480.jpeg/2zIsIl2zikOZ4o8LDrTD4SNInELiEo-5ji3mfo4t5n4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343033738336276480.jpeg%2F2zIsIl2zikOZ4o8LDrTD4SNInELiEo-5ji3mfo4t5n4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=234803f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然阿侯斯有近120年歷史，但這支老牌球會絕不古板，除了在看台空置的位置上，放置卡通造型的紙板球迷。他們亦在看台安置一個虛擬觀眾席，裝上一個長40米及高3米的大螢幕，讓一眾在賽前免費登記的球迷們，透過視像會議軟件Zoom在現場觀戰，容納近一萬名球迷。<br />\n<br />\n縱然阿侯斯球迷透過Zoom安在家中觀戰，但不少球迷「一家大細」齊集在電視前，更穿上阿侯斯球衣支持愛隊，可惜阿侯斯未能在主場全取3分，主隊在完場前由莫坦臣（Patrick Mortensen）射入扳平一球，結果兩軍打成1：1平手，阿侯斯以41分，僅次於米迪蘭特及哥本哈根暫列第3位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343033740907384832.jpeg/wdyKMgLkgyazNMmXGReqScPHRy8516B5WBNUmlgTVJo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343033740907384832.jpeg%2FwdyKMgLkgyazNMmXGReqScPHRy8516B5WBNUmlgTVJo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0bdd4576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343033745940549632.jpeg/E48UXZf2tcvD3AM6FpUIN-kqKVOMLMClbhqkLW4apC0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343033745940549632.jpeg%2FE48UXZf2tcvD3AM6FpUIN-kqKVOMLMClbhqkLW4apC0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b44d8585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343033753569988608.jpeg/VJP_t6ZkmfbbA9mgC3oyk6uYh0DgkmRM3Krcd9yq3Hc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343033753569988608.jpeg%2FVJP_t6ZkmfbbA9mgC3oyk6uYh0DgkmRM3Krcd9yq3Hc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=44d5593d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52277807c04ebbe2a23b61b32645df94f5c0e932","tid":2043229,"uid":168522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"客隊教練：陣間同我一腳射落個screen到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8dcc89cd66662eef9f8e1f32341682676a5886","tid":2043229,"uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:58:42.000Z","msg":"Zoom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfefe37dd5839e6786e2f6b4de8baffeb34814c","tid":2043229,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"香港本地波學下野啦"},{"pid":"79fe79f57eb7ac04d0e95d9c96b6669aabe401e2","tid":2043229,"uid":71833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0